{% if use_auth %}
## Auth Endpoints

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Exchange email+password for tokens |
| POST | `/api/auth/refresh` | Exchange refresh_token for a new access_token |
| POST | `/api/auth/logout` | Invalidate the current refresh token |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Return the currently authenticated user |

### POST /api/auth/login

Request:
```json
{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}
```

Response (200):
```json
{
  "token": "<jwt-access-token>",
  "refresh_token": "<refresh-token>",
  "user": {
    "id": "018e7b1a-...",
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "name": "Jane Smith",
    "roles": ["ROLE_USER"]
  }
}
```

