## Versioning Policy

The API is currently unversioned (no `/v1/` prefix). When a breaking change is needed:

1. Write an ADR explaining the breaking change
2. Add the new endpoint at a `/v2/` path
3. Deprecate the old path with a `Deprecation` response header
4. Remove the old path only after all consumers are updated

Non-breaking changes (new optional fields, new endpoints) do not require versioning and can be deployed freely.
